Events.Text: Not again! You took the wrong bus and got totally lost in the middle of the city. But you have to get to your job interview in time! Ask you personal AI assistant for help. [instruction 1 of 5]
Hello
The job interview is somewhere near Hospital. If you can get there, you should know your way again. [instruction 2 of 5]
hi
Hello, how can I help?
I'm lost! I took the wrong bus and got lost in the middle of the city- and I'm on my way to an important interview! Please help!

Follow the way-instructions of the assistant and imagine you do what it says. But your sense of orientation is pretty bad and you cannot deal with instructions involving 'North', 'West', 'South', 'East'. So if that comes up, ask for more details. [instruction 3 of 5]
arrival location
Where do you need to go?
Hospital - if I can get there, I know how to find my way.
travel mode
Do you want to drive, walk, or use public transit?
Transport, please.
departure time
When are you going to start your trip?
Right now.
Complain about the general situation, make a joke, or say something about the environment you imagine yourself in right now. [instruction 4 of 5]
